# Python Demo Web

A standard Python FastAPI web project for file-upload workflows.

## Project Layout

```text
app/
  api/routes/      HTTP route handlers
  core/            settings and application configuration
  schemas/         request and response models
  services/        reusable business logic and external adapters
tests/             pytest test suite
test2.py           backward-compatible CLI entry
```

## Setup

```bash
python3 -m venv .venv
source .venv/bin/activate
python3 -m pip install -e ".[dev]"
```

## Run

```bash
uvicorn app.main:app --reload
```

Health check:

```bash
curl http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/health
```

## Test

```bash
python3 -m pytest
```

